Quote: Senior citizens will be able to enjoy a free cup of tea or coffee when they chow down on a hamburger with fast-food chain McDonalds joining the SuperGold card scheme.The SuperGold card, launched in August, is a discount card for pensioners that offers improved rates and services from about 700 businesses that have so far signed up to it.
